with info    last 20140203
with version stable 5.86 5.85 5.84
with base    perl--ExtUtils-ParseXS
with switch  -t '' to build a thread-safe version of the module
with switch  -x '' to exclude support for SHA-384/512
with role    perl
with trait   perl-module
with source  stable http://www.cpan.org/authors/id/M/MS/MSHELOR/Digest-SHA-$VERSION.tar.gz
with info    home http://search.cpan.org/search?dist=Digest-SHA
with info    cite 'complete implementation of the NIST Secure Hash Standard
It gives Perl programmers a convenient way to calculate
SHA-1, SHA-224, SHA-256, SHA-384, and SHA-512 message digests.
The module can handle all types of input, including partial-byte data.'
